Class DefaultMockEc2Instance

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tlswe.awsmock.ec2.model.AbstractMockEc2Instance
      • com.tlswe.awsmock.ec2.model.DefaultMockEc2Instance
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class DefaultMockEc2Instance
extends AbstractMockEc2Instance
    Default type of mock ec2 instance (extends AbstractMockEc2Instance), using a timer to mock the lifecycle of instance.

      • onInternalTimer

        public void onInternalTimer()
        Description copied from class: AbstractMockEc2Instance
        Triggered on arriving interval of the internal timer of mock ec2 instance.
        Note that if this method does things that take a long time, the interval would be prolonged and consequent events/state changing would always be delayed.
